 to the Neo Geo Pocket Color in 2000. Due to hardware limitations the Neo Geo Pocket Color features less detailed graphics and sound compared to previous versions, however it is still a faithful version of the original in terms of gameplay.","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/cotton-fantastic-night-dreams","videos":[{"id":135598,"video_id":"w_8Bv83WEsE"}],"websites":[{"id":358642,"url":"https://www.twitch.tv/directory/game/Cotton","type":{"id":6,"type":"Twitch"}},{"id":569536,"url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cotton:_Fantastic_Night_Dreams","type":{"id":3,"type":"Wikipedia"}},{"id":698664,"url":"https://shmups.wiki/library/Cotton:_Fantastic_Night_Dreams","type":{"id":2,"type":"Community Wiki"}}]}